        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "在提尔比茨的邀约下，来到了港区附近的某处高台",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "百忙之中能抽身陪我，实在是荣幸。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "对了，今天有个东西，想让你陪我一起看。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "北极星？",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "say": "提尔比茨用手指向了天空",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "嗯，Polarstern。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "每当看见这颗星星，我就会想起那个时候，作为“存在舰队”而一直待在那个港口的自己。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "寒冷，孤独，这些我早已视为无物。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "最后，什么也做不了，只能在港口绝望地看着天空，迎来自己的终局。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "很可笑吧，这样的结局。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "……",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "但是，现在不一样了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "与人交流时的愉快，有人陪伴时的心脏的鼓动……这些心情，充满了温暖，像是要把所有寒冷与孤独融化一般燃烧着。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "“孤独的北方女王”，已经不再孤独了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果，梦中的“另一个我”，能像现在这样的话就好了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "啊啊，我感觉有点累了。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "肩膀上传来了重量",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "稍微……让我依靠一下吧。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
